<HEADLINE> Greek Communist Party Opposes New NATO Doctrine </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, April 26 (Xinhua) -- The Secretary-General of the
Communist Party of Greece (KKE) Aleka Papariga Monday expressed
her opposition to a new doctrine adopted by NATO on Saturday which
finally breaks original collective defense doctrine and assumes
broader functions to take actions outside alliance territory.
</P>
