Speaking after meeting with Greece's main opposition New
Democracy (ND) leader Costas Karamanlis on developments in Kosovo,
Papariga said that the new NATO doctrine had to be opposed by all
because it undermined every notion of popular or national
sovereignty, the semi-official Athens News Agency (ANA) reported.
