<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, April 27 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock Exchange
National-100 Index closed at 5,295.64 points on Tuesday, down 9.49
points, or 0.17 percent, from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was heavy with the turnover reaching 160 trillion
Turkish Liras (418 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 8.30 points, or 0.12 percent, to
close at 7,254.95 points, the services index fell 176.72 points,
or 2.89 percent, to close at 5,972.29 points while the industrial
index rose 33.30 points, or 1.01 percent, to close at 3,411.06
points. 
