dollars an ounce from Monday's close of 283.35 U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
National turnover was 490.49 million shares at a value of 775.8
million dollars.
</P>
<P>
There were 641 rises compared with 699 falls while 489 stocks
remained steady. 
