<P>
Prior to environmental control project, Yang Haiming and his
colleagues visited the Kunming International Horticultural
Exposition gardens, about six kilometers northeast of Kunming City
proper. "It is green everywhere, very beautiful" Yang said. "we
were deeply touched and resolved to turn the garbage dumping site
into an 'oxygen bar'."
