<HEADLINE> Share Prices Close Higher on Singapore Stock Market </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, April 27 (Xinhua) -- Share prices closed higher on
Singapore Stock Market Tuesday with mixed shares and blue-chips
holding ground on foreign funds inflow.
</P>
