<HEADLINE> Indonesian Badminton Queen Susi Susanti Gives Birth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, April 27 (Xinhua) -- Indonesia's former badminton
queen Susi Susanti gave birth to a baby girl through Caesarean
section at the Medistra Hospital here Monday.
</P>
<P>
