<HEADLINE> Helicopter Maintenance Soldier Commended by PLA (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Even foreign helicopter experts came all the way to China to
discuss these tail propeller issues with Li after reading his
paper.
</P>
<P>
He also found out on several occasions the cause of such
accidents as engine failure in large scale military training
operations that had not been discovered by technicians with formal
higher education.
</P>
<P>
In the past few years, his 16 papers on helicopter maintenance
and character improvement were published in state-level magazines
or collected by high level symposiums on helicopters.
</P>
<P>
Invited as a member of the experts group in his unit, the
soldier was also invited to give a lecture in Beijing University
of Aeronautics and Astronautics, the country's top university in
the field last month.
